data.eml:eml: Exploring unknown life stages of Arctic Tanytarsini (Diptera: Chironomidae) with DNA barcoding

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Stur, Elisabeth, Ekrem, Torbjørn (2011): Exploring unknown life stages of Arctic Tanytarsini (Diptera: Chironomidae) with DNA barcoding. Zootaxa 2743: 27-39, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.205429
